snippet.title: Magical Drop F - Daibouken Mo Rakujyanai! - Hard
snippet.description:
I finally got to emulating Playstation games, and immediately decided to play the one Magical Drop game I'd not get the chance to play by regular means: "Magical Drop F".

This game was unique from the rest of the games in the franchise for its more anime-esque design, as well as the addition of special abilities that are unique to each character.

I play through Battle Mode on Hard difficulty, clearing all opponents without losing.

Character: Justice
